rabbitmq:index/policy:Policy.description:
The ``rabbitmq..Policy`` resource creates and manages policies for exchanges
and queues.

## Example Usage

```typescript
import * as pulumi from "@pulumi/pulumi";
import * as rabbitmq from "@pulumi/rabbitmq";

const testVHost = new rabbitmq.VHost("test", {});
const guest = new rabbitmq.Permissions("guest", {
    permissions: {
        configure: ".*",
        read: ".*",
        write: ".*",
    },
    user: "guest",
    vhost: testVHost.name,
});
const testPolicy = new rabbitmq.Policy("test", {
    policy: {
        applyTo: "all",
        definition: {
            "ha-mode": "all",
        },
        pattern: ".*",
        priority: 0,
    },
    vhost: guest.vhost,
});
```

> This content is derived from https://github.com/terraform-providers/terraform-provider-rabbitmq/blob/master/website/docs/r/policy.html.markdown.

rabbitmq:index/queue:Queue.description:
The ``rabbitmq..Queue`` resource creates and manages a queue.

## Example Usage

### Basic Example

```typescript
import * as pulumi from "@pulumi/pulumi";
import * as rabbitmq from "@pulumi/rabbitmq";

const testVHost = new rabbitmq.VHost("test", {});
const guest = new rabbitmq.Permissions("guest", {
    permissions: {
        configure: ".*",
        read: ".*",
        write: ".*",
    },
    user: "guest",
    vhost: testVHost.name,
});
const testQueue = new rabbitmq.Queue("test", {
    settings: {
        autoDelete: true,
        durable: false,
    },
    vhost: guest.vhost,
});
```

### Example With JSON Arguments

```typescript
import * as pulumi from "@pulumi/pulumi";
import * as rabbitmq from "@pulumi/rabbitmq";

const config = new pulumi.Config();
const arguments = config.get("arguments") || `{
  "x-message-ttl": 5000
}
`;

const testVHost = new rabbitmq.VHost("test", {});
const guest = new rabbitmq.Permissions("guest", {
    permissions: {
        configure: ".*",
        read: ".*",
        write: ".*",
    },
    user: "guest",
    vhost: testVHost.name,
});
const testQueue = new rabbitmq.Queue("test", {
    settings: {
        argumentsJson: arguments,
        autoDelete: true,
        durable: false,
    },
    vhost: guest.vhost,
});
```

